# Preparedness That Works When It Matters

## Tested Through Real Emergencies, Not Just Reviews

When Hurricane Francine knocked out power across the South for five days, we learned what actually works versus what just looks good in product photos. SafeHarborPrep shares that hard-earned knowledge—real testing, honest limitations, practical solutions.

**We test what we review.** Every product recommendation comes from actual use during power outages, severe weather, and rural living where help isn't coming quickly.

